data.description: Don't miss this chance to own a slice of Southwestern paradise. Embrace the opportunity to restore and personalize this 2 bedroom 2 bathroom ranch Santa Fe style home, transforming it into the residence you've always dreamed of. For animal lovers, this property is a dream come true. The presence of a loafing shed means that your four-legged friends, whether horses or other livestock, have a comfortable shelter. Imagine the joy of watching your horses roam freely against the backdrop of wide-open spaces. Rest easy knowing that this home is equipped with a well-fed water tank featuring a float system. With over 238 acres of breathtaking land at your disposal, the possibilities are as vast as the endless horizon that stretches before you!
